---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Curated FAQ Lists"
permalink: "/lists/"
---

<div class="curated-lists-intro">
  <h3>Curated FAQ lists</h3>
  <p>Curated collections of FAQs for specific topics and audiences. These lists includes questions and answers covering all aspects of the Cyber Resilience Act as it relates to open source.</p>
  <p><strong>Note:</strong> These list includes FAQs regardless of their completion status. Some entries may be drafts, have missing content, or require additional guidance.
</div>

<div class="curated-lists-grid">
  {% for listId in site.listOrder %}
    {% for list in data.lists %}
      {% if list.id == listId %}
        <a href="{{ list.permalink }}" class="curated-list-card">
          <h2 class="list-title">
            {% if list.icon %}
              <span class="list-icon">{{ list.icon }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            {{ list.title }}
          </h2>
          <p class="list-description">{{ list.description }}</p>
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  {% endfor %}
</div>

